1. Why CSS?
Clean way to separate content and design
1 content can have multiple styles
Switching style is easy

2. Default CSS stylesheet
If no styling specified, default to Modena, located in JavaFX JAR file

3. Scene CSS stylesheet
Style applied to all JavaFX components added to scene graph for that scene object

4. Parent-specific CSS stylesheet
Style applied on parent and all its components inside

5. Component CSS stylesheet
Style directly applied on component